# Configuration Reference

This page documents all available configuration options for {{ project_name }}.

## File Locations

| File | Purpose |
|------|---------|
| `.env` | Environment variables |
| `pyproject.toml` | Python project configuration |
| `package.json` | Node.js workspace configuration |
| `docusaurus.config.ts` | Documentation site configuration |

## pyproject.toml

The main Python configuration file:

```toml
[project]
name = "{{ package_name }}"
version = "0.1.0"
requires-python = ">=3.11"

[tool.ruff]
line-length = 88
target-version = "py311"

[tool.mypy]
python_version = "3.11"
strict = true
```

## docusaurus.config.ts

Key Docusaurus configuration options:

| Option | Type | Description |
|--------|------|-------------|
| `title` | string | Site title |
| `tagline` | string | Site tagline |
| `url` | string | Production URL |
| `baseUrl` | string | Base URL path |
| `onBrokenLinks` | string | Behavior on broken links |
{%- if docusaurus_faster == 'enabled' %}
| `future.experimental_faster` | object | Performance optimizations |
{%- endif %}
{%- if docusaurus_i18n == 'enabled' %}
| `i18n` | object | Internationalization config |
{%- endif %}

